Diebold Inc Partners With Infosys And Oracle To Transform Business Operations
Thursday, 7 Nov 2013 09:00am EST
Diebold Inc announced that it has partnered with Infosys and Oracle to deploy enterprise applications. Diebold has more than 10 years of Oracle enterprise resource planning (ERP) experience, and has partnered with Infosys over the past 18 months to strategize, mobilize and transform its global information technology (IT) delivery. By deploying Oracle's enterprise applications, Diebold will simplify and standardize its global processes to create a more robust and customer-centric enterprise. The enterprise applications (Oracle R12 E-business suite and Siebel Field Service) will drive internal efficiencies and enable an integrated real-time view of Diebold's global cross-functional processes and data.Â 
